Installation
------------

```bash
nix-shell -p git --run "git clone https://github.com/bartekzer/nix-config.git /wherever/you/want"
```

Usage
-----

```bash
sudo nixos-rebuild switch --flake /path/to/configuration --impure
# or on the next boot
sudo nixos-rebuild boot --flake /path/to/configuration --impure
```
